headline: Dollar Tree Stock Is Soaring. Is This the Time to Buy?
summary: Dollar Tree is approaching a 52-week high.  Once the Family Dollar brand is gone, Dollar Tree will be able to focus on its core business.  Shares of Dollar Tree (NASDAQ: DLTR) are up more than 60% since mid-March and are fast approaching a 52-week high.
